snippet.title: 1914: The Great War - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Recorded by Ownederd.

"1914: The Great War" is a turned-based RTT game published by JoWooD Entertainment and developed by TriNodE Entertainment Systems.

This gameplay video shows a failed skirmish between me (Germany) and France (AI) in the main German campaign.
